title: SuRie - Storm (United Kingdom Eurovision 2018) [Video].mpeg
description:
SuRie - Storm MPEG2 1080 Audio 320 kbps 

This is the studio video of the UK entry for Eurovision 2018.  It is a class pop song and should do well.

Along with the Maltese Entry by Christabelle - Taboo both songs are great value at the bookmakers right now with odds of 67 to 1 for the UK and over 2000 to 1 for tiny little Malta.

As a professional working in the Music industry since 1967 and supporting Eurovision since 1969 if you have a little cash to spare on a flutter these two are the best of this years crop as far as just sheer stick you our head re singability goes.  And that is my litmus test for a Eurovision Winner
